radioButtons - Variable in class MultiQuizFrame.RadioPane
The JRadioButton[] radioButton is an array of the JRadioButtons corresponding to the possible answers of the question.
radioGroup - Variable in class MultiQuizFrame.RadioPane
The ButtonGroup radioGroup contains the JRadioButtons corresponding to the possible answers of the question, and serves to make only one of the JRadioButtons able to selected at a given time.
RadioPane(Integer, Integer) - Constructor for class MultiQuizFrame.RadioPane
The RadioPane constructor takes an Integer questionNum and an Integer numRadioButtons and gives the RadioPane a questionLabel corresponding to the question text, a nextButton to change to the next tab, and makes radioButtons of the amount specified by numRadioButtons.
RadPaneButtonhandler() - Constructor for class MultiQuizFrame.RadioPane.RadPaneButtonhandler
 
resetRightList - Variable in class MultiQuizFrame.JListPane
The JButton moveListRightButton moves the selected values form the fromList to the toList and the JButton resetRightList clears the contents of the toList so the user can re-add selected items.
resizeImgToIcon(int, int, String) - Method in class MultiQuizFrame
The resizeImgtoIcon() method takes a filename corresponding to a png and resizes it to the dimensions width and height specified in the function parameters.
